Package: parmesan
Title: Parametrized Shiny Apps... Neat!
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Juan Pablo",
           family = "Marin Diaz",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jpmarindiaz@gmail.com")
Maintainer: Juan Pablo Marin Diaz <jpmarindiaz@gmail.com>
Description: Create shiny apps using configuration files to define
  inputs. Configuration files work by providing a layout and shiny
  inputs in plain text yaml files.
